[[div style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .8); padding: 5px;"]]
The Broadcast Alliance Entertainment Holdings is a multinational media production and distribution company headquartered in Japan. Most known for its high stakes combat gameshow, [[[the-extraction|THE EXTRACTION (ジ・エクストラクション)]]], the Broadcast Alliance stands as the world’s leading provider of entertainment, both above and below the board.
[[/div]]



